Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 547-548
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=Man Created for Contemplation
  - 847
By: Thomas Traherne
---
For you are never your true self, till you live by your soul more than
by your body, and you never live by your soul till you feel its
incomparable excellency, and rest satisfied and delighted in the
unsearchable greatness of its comprehension.
